{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_51_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 葵に贈るプレゼント",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "バレエもなし。フラダンスもフラメンコもなし。タップ\nダンスもチアもなし。残るは社交ダンスと……うーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No ballet. No hula‚ no flamenco‚ no tap dance‚\nand no cheerleading. The only things left are ballroom dancing and… hmmm",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "せめて、もう一つくらい種類を増やしたいわよね……\nそういえば、前にこころが……。よし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like to add at least one more type…\nCome to think of it‚ Kokoro tried… Alright…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ……雪よー、降りたまえー……！\nほんにゃらほんにゃら、ズンドコズンドコ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S‚ snowー Please come down~!\nHonnyara honnyara‚ zundoko zundoko…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4333324433,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3300.0002543000023,
          "startTime": 31.7333326976
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "何してるの、莉央？\nこんな夜遅くに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you doing‚ Rio?\nSo late at night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでもないわよ！　誰かさんの困ったお願いを\n叶えるために、いろいろ試行錯誤してるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nothing! I'm trying all sorts of things\nto grant someone's troublesome request.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん、莉央をこんなに悩ませるなんて\n酷いやつだね。一度僕が怒ってあげようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm‚ making Rio this worried…\nWhat a terrible person. Should I scold them for you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ぜひ怒ってほしいわね。こころと共謀して\n私と愛をドッキリにハメようとする生意気な子を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd definitely like you to scold them.\nA cheeky girl trying to trick Ai and me with a prank‚ with Kokoro’s help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、気付いてたんだ。ネタバラシはまだなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you noticed. I haven't even revealed the punchline yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3333304088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに気付いたわよ。偶然にしては出来過ぎてるし\nタップダンスとチアダンスを習った時なんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I noticed. It's too much of a coincidence.\nEven when we learned tap dance and cheerleading‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "隠し撮りどころか、こころってば丸見えで撮ってたわよ\n本人と愛は気付いてないみたいだったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro wasn't even secretly filming… She was filming in plain sight.\nShe and Ai didn't seem to notice though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……ここまできて、野暮なことはしないわ\n今のは全部独り言よ。忘れてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I'm not going to be a wet blanket after coming this far.\nEverything I said was just me talking to myself. Please forget it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.066670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "私、神崎莉央は何も気付いてないし\nきっと当日も、凄く驚くと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ Kanzaki Rio‚ haven't noticed anything‚\nand I'm sure I'll be really surprised on the day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.0666681925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。じゃあ、これも独り言だけど、後でこころには\n注意しておかないとね。もっと忍者らしく身を隠せって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Then‚ and this is also just me talking to myself. I should warn\nKokoro later to hide herself more like a ninja.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0666671752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "忍者って。どういう設定なのよ、それ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A ninja? What kind of setting is that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5333166758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "隠れて動向を探ったり、雑誌の記事に使うための\n写真を撮ったりする、忍者の役だよ。面白いでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A ninja who hides and gathers information or takes\nphotos for magazine articles. It's a ninja's role. It's fun‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6333338419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、でも本人は\n「美人スパイの方がいいです～」って言ってたかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ but she said\n\"A beautiful spy would be better~‚\" or something like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3999959308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "どっちでもいいわよ。ただ……それより気になるのは\nなんで企画の内容をドッキリにしたのかってことね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Either way is fine. But… what I'm more curious about is…\nwhy you made the project content a prank.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.599992879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "いかにもこころが好きそうな内容だし\n本人もノリノリで参加してるし。いい先輩が過ぎるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just the type of thing Kokoro likes‚\nand she's also participating enthusiastically. You're being too good of a senior.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.5009939056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "当日は、どうしてもこころが参加出来ないからね\nそれまでに、一緒に楽しめる内容にしたかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ Kokoro can't participate on the actual day no matter what.\nI wanted to make the content something we could all enjoy together by then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8333262124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "この誕生日企画自体、星見プロの中では僕が最後だし\nリズノワ四人揃って、ラストを飾りたかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm the last one in Hoshimi Pro for this birthday project.\nSo‚ I wanted LizNoir to have all four members together to decorate the finale.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2999755857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "二人だけの頃だったら\nもっと好き放題、自由にやっていたんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it was just the two of us‚\nwouldn't you have done whatever you wanted more freely?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3333028154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね。でも莉央や{user}君のおかげで\n普段から十分自由にやらせてもらってるし。構わないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah. But thanks to Rio and {user}-kun‚\nI've been allowed to do whatever I want freely anyway‚ so I don't mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.5333017982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "そう。葵がいいなら……って言いたいところだけど\n私はあまり、納得出来ないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. It's fine if you are okay with it… is what I want to say but\nI'm not really convinced.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.8332824703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.5665986375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "葵の気持ちは尊重するわ。台無しにしたりはしない\nでも、長年付き添ってきた相手の誕生日を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I respect your feelings‚ Aoi. I won't ruin them.\nBut I don't want to end the birthday of someone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.9558645017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "後輩のためってだけで終わらせたくないの。だから――\n当日は、私が貴方に初めてのダンスを踊らせてあげるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been with for years just for the sake of juniors. So—\nOn that day‚ I'm going to make you dance a dance you've never done before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.5666066483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "--On the day of the photoshoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.033273315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.0665969482
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.0665969482
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.233269246
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.666616821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "（あれはどういう意味だったんだろう。そんなことが）\n（出来たら、嬉しいけど……いや、考えるのはよそう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What did that mean? If such a thing were to）\n（happen‚ I'd be happy‚ but… no‚ I shouldn't think about it.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.6999501543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.3999501543
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.3332520799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央はともかく、愛は気付いてなかったみたいだし）\n（こころのためにも、台本通りドッキリを仕掛けないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rio aside‚ it doesn't seem like Ai noticed.）\n（For Kokoro's sake‚ I have to pull off the surprise like the script.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.2332834877,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9566.6727702,
          "startTime": 227.7999562579
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 222.9499187466
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "今日は踊ったことないダンスを踊らせてくれるんだよね\n先生は……って、莉央と愛？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going to get to dance a dance I've never done before today‚ right?\nThe teachers are… Wait‚ Rio and Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.9999572752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "葵は『今まで踊ったことのないダンスを踊りたい』って\nお願いしたそうね。だから、私達で準備しておいたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"A dance that you've never done before.\"\nThat's what you asked‚ Aoi. So‚ we've prepared something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.4332834877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスを教えるのは私達よ。まずは社交ダンスから\nさぁ、手を出してちょうだい。私がリードしてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're the ones who will be teaching you the dance. Let's start with ballroom dancing.\nCome on‚ give me your hand. I'll lead you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.9999542233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "社交ダンスか。確かに、リードされたことはないかもね\nどっちかって言うと、リードする方が好きだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ballroom dancing‚ huh? Come to think of it‚ I've never been led before.\nTo be honest‚ I prefer to lead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.366616821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、手を出して、お姫様\n僕がリードしてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ give me your hand‚ princess.\nI'll lead you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.2332834877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ちょっ、誰がお姫様よ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? H-Hey‚ who are you calling a princess!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.9666261033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　葵さん、社交ダンスの経験あったんですか？\nというか流れで私が教える予定のダンスも踊ってる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? Aoi-san‚ have you had experience with ballroom dancing?\nWait‚ you're even doing the dance that I was supposed to teach you as well!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.0666188555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、じゃーん。ドッキリでしたー\n実は、莉央達が準備してたことは全部知ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And so‚ ta-da! It was a surprise~\nActually‚ I knew everything that you two were planning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.9999521889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "だからいろいろ先回りして、二人を驚かせたって訳\nこころと編集部の人達に手伝ってもらったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I did a lot of things in advance to surprise you two.\nKokoro and the people from the editorial department helped me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.0999501543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "ぜ、全然気付きませんでした。サプライズするつもりが\n逆にサプライズを仕掛けられちゃってたなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I didn't notice at all. We intended to surprise you‚\nbut we were the ones who got surprised instead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 302.866616821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "私も全然気付かなかったわ。こころまで参加してた\nなんて、結局リズノワ四人、全員関わっていたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't realize it at all either. Even Kokoro was participating.\nTo think that in the end‚ all four members of LizNoir were involved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.266616821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ごめんね。でも莉央と愛が僕のために頑張って\nくれて、本当に嬉しいよ。ありがとう、二人とも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ sorry. But Rio and Ai worked hard for me‚\nand I'm really happy. Thank you‚ you two.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.6332834877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "気にしなくていいわよ。私達も、きっとこころも\n葵に喜んでほしくてやってたんだから。良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to worry about it. We‚ and I'm sure Kokoro too‚\nwere doing it because we wanted Aoi to be happy. I'm glad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 329.0332977292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、せっかくだし、三人で踊ってみない？\nお互い、いろいろなダンスを習ったことだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ we've gone to all this trouble‚ so why don't we try dancing together?\nWe've both learned all sorts of dances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 337.4666310625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど僕も、同じことを言おうと思ってたんだ\nそれじゃあ最初はどれにする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was just about to say the same thing.\nSo‚ which one should we start with?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 344.266629028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、とびっきりのがあるわよ\n私が考えてきた『オリジナルのダンス』が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I've got something really special.\nThe \"original dance\" that I've been thinking about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.4332956947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "え……えぇぇぇぇぇ！？\nそんな話、初めて聞きましたよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Huh?!\nI've never heard of such a thing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 356.7999623613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "伝えてなくて悪かったわ。急に思い立ったことだったし\nでも、楽しいと思うわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for not telling you. It was something I thought of suddenly.\nBut I think it'll be fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 364.7677434229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろなダンスに触れた経験を生かして作った\n今までのリズノワのダンスとも違う、新作だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a new dance inspired by my experience with various dance styles‚\nunlike anything LizNoir has done before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 370.7333241777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "今までのリズノワとも違う、莉央が考えたダンス……\n僕のためだけに、作ってくれたダンス……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A dance Rio created‚ different from anything LizNoir has done before…\nA dance that she created just for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 381.1333241777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "凄いよ、莉央。驚かせるつもりだったのに\n今は僕の方が、何倍も驚いてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're amazing‚ Rio. I was planning to surprise you‚\nbut right now I'm the one who's many times more surprised…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 390.4666575111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "愛、準備はいい？　早く踊りたくてうずうずしてるんだ\nこの気持ちを全部、ダンスに乗せたいくらいに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ are you ready? I'm itching to dance already.\nI want to put all of this feeling into the dance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 400.0333424882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも、お二人のお邪魔になっちゃうんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But‚ won't I just be intruding on you two…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 403.6666484827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "見てるだけじゃもったいないよ\nいっそ、今日は一日中ずっと踊っていたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a waste to just watch.\nI wish I could just dance all day today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 410.5333424882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_03-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "まだ始めてもいないのに、気が早いわよ\nそれに、夜は寮で誕生日会があるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're getting ahead of yourself when we haven't even started yet.\nBesides‚ there's a birthday party at the dorm tonight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 417.4978511323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
